Here at Fenrir Canine Leaders we are all about helping dogs and their owners to have the best lives together possible. Fenrir is for you and your dog. We achieve this through our incredible range of products, designed from the perspective of a canine behaviourist, to fulfil all the needs of the everyday dog owner, whilst keeping your dog’s comfort and happiness in mind.

We have a wide range of products designed to facilitate and encourage long and happy relationships between owners and their dogs. Take our Ragnar Range for example. A range of leads, collar and harness all designed to be as comfortable, durable and flexible as possible to help both the owner and the dog master everyday life. Our flagship product, the Fenrir Hammer is as much training tool as it is dog toy, designed to encourage appropriate chewing behaviour and provide much needed mental stimulation whilst also being incredibly fun and engaging for all dogs. Each Fenrir product benefits both you and your dog from a practical and behavioural perspective.

INVENTOR STORY
Victor C. Talavera, is the inventor of the Split-Ender PRO. Mr. Talavera had a long hair and used to spend about 4 hours cutting off the split ends every two months with traditional scissors.

Thinking about how he could managed to speed up this process, he decided to invent an easy-to-use hair tool that could achieve the removal of damaged hair tips in just minutes without affecting the length of the hair. The urgent need for this technology gave birth to a revolutionary hair tool called the "Split-Ender PRO". Thanks to this product millions of men and women can now enjoy a long, soft and healthier hair better than ever before.

This new exciting beauty tool has provided professionals around the world with an additional profitable service that can be offer to clients. Not only Victor Talavera designed an easy to use "at home" hair tool but he also in the process revolutionized an industry for the long term.

About
Kylie Martin, along with her partner Garry, founded GK Gluten Free Foods in 2009, supplying Australian customers with the very first oats that were uncontaminated by the gluten found in wheat, rye and barley. Kylie’s interest in this product was the result of catering to a family plagued by various special dietary requirements, coupled with a passion for her farming heritage.

 

Since the beginning, it has been Kylie's dream to partner with Aussie farmers and offer uncontaminated oats grown right here in Australia. After 13 years of being in business, this dream finally became a reality in 2021 when GF Oats partnered with Australian farmers who specialise in growing and processing oats in a clean, uncontaminated environment, ensuring that they test to nil gluten from wheat, rye and barley. Our signature range of Gloriously Free steamed rolled oats are now proudly sourced from Avena Mills Australian farmers. These are the only oats in Australia that are tested, certified, and guaranteed to meet the strict Australian standards with regards to nil gluten detected from the contamination from wheat, rye or barley. 

Gloriously Free Oats follow the Global Oats Purity Protocol ensuring they are pure oats. Other countries have different labelling requirements around oats, however in Australia, current labelling laws continue to prevent us from labelling these oats as gluten-free oats. All of our oats are tested independently, right here in Australia for contamination at independent laborities.

At GK Gluten Free Foods we are driven by our commitment to offer products that you can trust to meet your specific dietary requirements. It is our belief that you can choose to “Live the Life That You Deserve” with our range of delicious and nutritious products that are Gloriously Free of the contamination from the gluten found in wheat, rye and barley.  

We are proudly 100% Australian Grown and Australian Owned and we are proud to call our oats "The Oats You Can Trust!". 

We invite you to find more about the GF Oats story, where we source our oats, and to explore our full range of products via our online shop. Please feel free to contact our team for further assistance. We provide prompt, safe and affordable delivery to all states in Australia!

OWL Stands for One Whole Life
The foundation of our company is founder, Lindsey Erin’s, personal journey to health. When her mother was diagnosed with breast cancer in 2010, Lindsey committed to living in a way that would minimize the risk of disease. It was this event that began her research on wellness, nutrition, and intuitive eating, and would eventually lead to the creation of OWL Venice.

Initially, Lindsey began experimenting with an organic, plant-based diet that limited meat and processed foods, and found that she was still experiencing constant allergy symptoms, digestive issues, and acne. In an attempt to resolve these issues, Lindsey began a diet geared to treat GAPS (Gut and Psychology Syndrome) which incorporated bone broth as a healing agent. After struggling to find pre-made broth that was void of common allergens, Lindsey began making her own bone broth with locally-sourced bones and an array of herbs and veggies. Through months of testing and development, she created a broth recipe that tasted more like a tea than a traditional stock, OWL’s signature flagship product.

OWL currently offers chicken, turkey, beef, bison, and vegan mineral Broth Elixirs that are sold throughout LA county, a 4, 6, and 8 day Reset cleanse program to heal and seal the gut, and an organic, oil-based skincare line. OWL also offers health coaching services with flexible sessions to fit your schedule and budget.

As more people discover the benefits of using OWL products, Lindsey & the OWL family will continue innovating, exploring, and sharing new ways to live better with those looking to transform their health and overall wellness.

Along with OWL’s mission to heal the body, OWL is also committed to healing the environment. This is why they maintain a minimal waste policy that requires the mylkshakes are made-to-order and the broths are pressure canned. All of OWL’s goods are packaged in glass, which is not only 100% recyclable, it is free of chemicals that could negatively impact the flavor and aroma of their products.

Our Story
Welcome to the KYOTI tribe.

 

"With KYOTI, I want to create meaningful jewellery that can be worn effortlessly and be handed down like a piece of treasure" 

founder Jodee Collett

KYOTI was born in the kaleidoscopic streets of India, the palm-fringed beaches of Thailand, the incense-scented markets of the middle east and beyond. After travelling the world for four years and creating beautiful jewellery along the way, Jodee realised that her passion could transition from sales at flea markets and festivals to a one-woman business based in her hometown of Melbourne.

 The name KYOTI came to Jodee in a dream, and to a wanderer whose childhood nickname was 'Jodee Coyote' it seemed all too perfect. The spelling is a play on Coyote, a spirit animal that's woven into the stories and legends of Native Americans and is associated with a deep magic in life and creation.

Today KYOTI has built a dedicated following of free-spirits across the globe. From barefoot gypsies to corporate honeys, the brand speaks to goddesses treading all paths of life.


From the spiritual significance of moon, ancient wisdom buried in symbolism and all the wonder associated with the cosmos, KYOTI pieces are inspired by an infatuation with the hidden treasures of our history on this earth. Creator Jodee Collett takes these hallowed meanings and blends them with a timeless aesthetic. The designs are strong, with subtle but very powerful meanings behind them. Intended to make their owner feel beautiful, sexy and free from social constructs. For the wild, magical and mystical babes.
When dreaming up her designs, Jodee strives to create jewellery that's not only beautiful but also empowers its wearer with a deeper meaning. In this sense, KYOTI pieces are more than just treasures. They're wearable talismans, a natural way to stand out from the crowd and reflect personal style while simultaneously serving as symbols of strength, wonder, beauty and womanhood.

To Jodee, nothing captures the magic of nature quite like raw gemstones. This is why the KYOTI collection is studded Grade A gemstones handpicked not only for their looks, but also for their intrinsic meaning. Whether it's the protective properties and inky hues of black onyx, the healing powers and soft feminine energy of rose quartz or the intense energy and Goddess vibes of rainbow moonstone, KYOTI pieces serve as daily reminders that organic divinity, sacredness and spirituality are ever-present. 

Jodee's artisan approach to her designs are showcased throughout the collection, whether it's intricate traditional dot work techniques, a beautifully set stone or hand-soldered gold embellishment. Every creation is approached like a true work of art – with incredible attention to detail, lashings of creativity and the total freedom to embrace imperfections. After all, each KYOTI piece is as unique as its wearer.

KYOTI pieces are made to last a lifetime. The highest grade of materials is used to ensure that pieces can serve not only their original wearer but be passed down as heirlooms. Daughters, nieces, soul sisters… KYOTI pieces not only tell a story but exist to serve as living talismans of your own experiences.

Of course, there's plenty of room for colour and creativity, which means there's no fear when it comes to mixing precious materials with natural elements that shine just as bright. Think 9 Carat Gold and rainbow moonstone. Sterling silver and smokey quartz crystals. Italian Brass and turquoise.

Book Therapy - the Modern Day Version of Bibliotherapy

Book therapy or bibliotherapy leverages the power of reading to support better mental health and wellbeing.  From the ancient Greeks to modern day millennials, reading literature has often been recognised as a therapeutic medium with curative effects that harness the power of creative storytelling, poetry, novellas, personal development and self-help books.

Here at Book Therapy we offer free book prescriptions for adults and children. Ordered in A - Z format, these recommended reading lists, 'what-to-read' digests, (what I fondly term "book prescriptions") have been hand-picked and collated for everything under the sun - whether you're looking for something therapeutic or for personal interest, these book recommendations are here to inspire, uplift and engage.

And if that's not enough, we also curate personalised reading lists (which can be for therapy or personal interest), offer bibliotherapy sessions for both individuals and couples, literary afternoon tea sessions and mini-bibliotherapy sessions at private parties, weddings and other events.

Our Story

By Nappers, For Nappers


The Plufl journey began when we realized there needed to be a better way to rest.

As tired college students, we took a lot of naps. But our issue? There weren't any comfortable places to nap on campus!

One day, we saw a large dog napping blissfully in a giant dog bed at our local college coffee shop.

That's when the idea struck us.

Dog beds ... but for HUMANS!!

From that day onwards, we embarked on our journey of bringing our idea to life. The result: a kickass napping product that's so comfortable we struggle to get out of it everyday.

We're so excited that you're here to join us on this journey and we can't wait to help you get that rest you deserve. 

Love,

Noah and Yuki 

Our Mission:

Delivering a Better Way to Rest

Plufl is on a mission to help you get the rest you deserve, wherever and whenever.

All of us experience stress and anxiety, and we wanted to create something that would help with that.

So, we embarked on a journey to create a product so comfy and cozy that you wouldn't help but smile when experiencing it.

Our creation? The Plufl. The world's first human dog bed.

This all started…
back in the 1970's when my mother owned her own embroidery business. This was before monograms were seen on bags, shoes, front doors, and cars. Her machine was about the size of a kitchen island! She perfected beautiful and classic embroidered monograms as I watched her over the years. Mom monogrammed everything we owned - sweaters, laundry bags, telephone book covers (remember those?), even my socks! Her monogrammed items can still be found in many homes throughout our community today.


Fast forward to 2015. After raising two wonderful children with my sweetheart and teaching high school math, I rediscovered my love for beautiful letters - only this time creating them digitally. I looked for new ways to enhance and modernize old monograms from long ago. Sifting through books of typefaces and monograms, I began creating new designs - ones that could represent the personality of the individual or business who owned them.

Shuler Studio launched in 2016. Three years later, I was blessed to have my amazing daughter join me! We love creating letters, monograms, and designs, and we hope you find something perfect for you. It is pure joy to see someone put our designs on their own piece of life - an invitation, a dance floor, a chair, a storefront window.  

My mom passed away in 2016, the same year Shuler Studio was launched. She missed seeing this business unfold but would have been amazed at how monograms and technology have evolved over the years. So I dedicate this venture to you, Mom. You would have loved to embroider these beautiful and unique designs on anything and everything - yes, even my socks!

About Us  

Tea has been the catalyst for revolutions in past times. The struggle that small farmers have had to be paid fairly and the injustices workers have faced has been present in the news for a long time. The Ethical Tea Revolution is an idea that is important to us as we and other growers fight against the injustice that has marked our past. Unethical practices are on its way out as we embrace social equality throughout the growing and selling of tea.


Organic Practices
Our associate small tea growers in Assam adhere to global standards of sustainable, organic farming methods. The range of teas we offer follow the strict standards set by India's National Programme for Organic Production (NPOP). 

The cultivation process is a small part of what it takes to get the teas from the grower to your table. Every aspect of the growing, picking and processing of these products is monitored to ensure ethical standards are met. We utilize ancient methods such as Vriksayurveda Organic Farming technique so that you get the finest quality teas, high in phyto-nutrients and free from the dangerous chemicals often used in the commercial production of teas. And, we never rely on mechanical processes. Every leaf of our tea is hand-picked and manually processed with lots of care. 


Hiring Workers at Fair Wages
It is common to see tea workers in Assam and other neighboring regions getting paid absurdly low wages for their hard work, even in this day and age. The unfair wages has resulted in social unrest in the region as workers demand fair pay. 

Here at ASSAMICA AGRO, we actively help our rural community by helping our associate farmers hire workers at fair wages, unaffected by the large conglomerates pressuring the area to underpay their workers to make a profit. Our farms have higher levels of worker pay than the average rate in Assam. The fair price we offer our associates allows them to afford fair wages for their hard-working employees. With every sale, we are helping to enhance our local economy by providing a real livelihood for farm workers, improving living standards in the region.


Protecting the Environment
Yes, we are creating good jobs as we protect our precious land. We are securing the future with sustainable land management. Through our work with small-scale, organic farmers in the North East region, we are creating a sustainable way of farming the land. We encourage the small tea farmers to plant other cash crops along with tea, so that the bio-diversity of the land is improved, allowing the soil to remain nutrient rich.


THERE IS A RIGHT WAY TO DO THINGS

The ASSAMICA AGRO Vision
We are a company that is helping to fight decades of unethical employment and bad practices that has led to poor land management in the region. We strive to revolutionize the tea growing in the Assam region. We provide some of the highest quality teas in the region and some of the healthiest teas on the market. Our farm workers have seen an improvement in their standard of living through our ethical practices. The land is seen as a precious resource that must last for future generations. 

The beginning of any revolution is filled with difficulty, but here at the ASSAMICA AGRO, we can already see the impact we have on the community. We, along with our associate growers, share a vision that through our growth, the importance we have on the local community increases as well, so that this troubled yet beautiful part of the world, will prosper with us... sustaining and protecting the land and its people.

Company
Established in 2010 as a private limited company, ASSAMICA AGRO is based in rural Assam and is committed to following ethical and organic farming standards. Our company also produces organic fruits, vegetables, traditional rice, rubber and milk in association with our small-scale organic farmers. Furthermore, we help to market the produce of other smaller tea & herbs growers in the region through our eCommerce website. We have a small resort inside our tea farm. Our guests can experience organic tea farming and manufacturing by staying in our farm Resort.


Address

OUR STORY: A JOURNEY OF LOVE, HOPE, AND BEAUTIFUL HAIR
Hi, I'm Jane, and I want to share a very personal journey with you—a journey that led to the birth of The Australian Organic. It's a journey of love, hope, and the dream of healthier, more beautiful hair for all. It's not just my journey; it's a journey many of us can relate to. It's about those moments when life surprises us, and we find ourselves in need of a little extra love and care, especially for our hair.

 

The Start of My Journey

It all began when I was 27. At that age, most people are focused on their careers, adventures, and dreams. I was too, but I was also facing something unexpected—a battle with Hashimoto's disease and an underactive thyroid. It was a diagnosis that changed my life in more ways than one.

As if dealing with a health condition wasn't challenging enough, something else started happening. I noticed it first in my hair, it began to thin, and with each strand that slipped away, a little piece of my confidence went with it.

 

The Search for Solutions

Desperation led me on a quest for answers. I turned to dermatologists and tried countless products they recommended. But no matter what I did, nothing seemed to work. It was disheartening, to say the least. And it turns out, I wasn't alone—so many men and women with autoimmune diseases faced the same struggle.

I had almost given up hope, but something inside me kept searching. So, I dived into research, read countless articles, and talked to professionals. I was on a mission to find a way to get my hair—and my confidence—back.

 

The Moment of Transformation

After months of trying different product formulas and countless hours of experimenting, something magical happened. My hair transformed right before my eyes. It felt thicker, stronger, and healthier than it had in years. I couldn't believe it; it was like a dream come true.

This transformation wasn't just about hair; it was about reclaiming my self-esteem and my joy. And that's when I realized that I couldn't keep this discovery to myself. There were others out there facing similar challenges, and I had to share the hope and the happiness that had come my way.

 

The Birth of The Australian Organic

My dream was born—to create products that weren't just effective but also safe, natural, and free from harsh chemicals. I wanted to turn back the clock on aging hair, promote vibrant, healthy locks, and prevent future hair struggles. I wanted everyone, no matter their age or story, to have their best hair ever.

So, after countless trials and a year of working closely with formulators, I created The Australian Organic. It's a range of natural hair care products that actually work, without any of the harsh chemicals. 

 

From Benchtop to Worldwide Beauty: Our Remarkable Journey

Our story began with a handful of products and a dream—Hair Growth Shampoo, Conditioner, and the amazing Argan Oil Hair Growth Serum. The response was overwhelming, and we quickly went from selling a few bottles a day to hundreds, then thousands, worldwide.

 

Global Reach

Today, we offer over 40 unique product bundles online, reaching customers in countries around the globe. With just a click from your phone or your computer, you can have our products delivered right to your doorstep, no matter where you are.

 

Caring for Our Planet

We're not just about beauty; we're also about responsibility. Our bottles are recyclable, our products are made using solar power, and our packing materials are biodegradable. We're dedicated to making a positive impact on our planet.

 

Our Journey: Where Diversity Shines

Our story isn't just about hair; it's about celebrating diversity and inclusion. At The Australian Organic, we believe in the power of every unique voice. Whether you're part of our team, a partner, or simply part of our extended family, we embrace diversity and welcome all backgrounds, identities, and beliefs.

 

Celebrating Uniqueness

Just as our products celebrate the uniqueness of your hair, we celebrate the uniqueness of each individual. It doesn't matter where you come from, your identity, or your beliefs – our doors are open to everyone. We're here to create a space where every voice is heard, every story is valued, and every person is respected. We believe that it's through our differences that we can create something truly remarkable. 

 

Joining Hands on This Caring Journey

At The Australian Organic, we invite you to be part of this personal caring journey. It's not just my story; it's a story of hope, transformation, and the belief that everyone deserves to love their hair. Beautiful, healthy hair isn't just a luxury—it's a right, and we're here to make it accessible to all.

So, here's to your hair's transformation, to newfound confidence, and to embracing your unique beauty. Welcome to The Australian Organic, where our story is your story, and where we believe that every day is an opportunity to shine a little brighter. We care deeply about you and your journey to beautiful, healthy hair.

HELLO THERE! 
We are Blagovest and Viktor, the team behind SaberMasters. For as long as we have been Star Wars fans, we’ve enjoyed acting out our favorite scenes and dueling with lightsabers. With that has come the frustration of triumphant moments ruined by a broken saber compounded by suppliers who were reluctant to respond to feedback from us, the fans. They’re willing to take our money but never listen to our attempts at communication.     


We wanted the best quality sabers and it became clear that only fans would listen to other fans and provide what fans want, so we had to do it ourselves. Fortunately, we had the high ground. We would apply our training as marketologists and knowledge of business to bring the highest quality sabers to the community with the best service in the Galaxy.   


A NEW HOPE   
The result of our efforts has been high-quality lightsabers that complement every Star Wars costume and battle reenactment. And yet, it surpassed our dreams — over 10,000 orders, most of them for two sabers, meaning some 15-20,000 fans have trusted our product. What is even more extraordinary than this number is the imagination and resourcefulness of our customers who find the most inventive of ways to use the sabers (and look awesome doing it). 


Since we are part of the Star Wars community, we value communication above all (yes, even above — *gasp* — the Force) and will always be here to talk you through everything — how to order your saber, how to wield it like a Master, and even how to return it if you have a bad feeling about it. 


We cannot teach you the ways of the Force, but we promise to supply you with the perfect weapon to channel it.

What does Bigly do?
Bigly is the absolute best in class at monetizing content creators. Why? Because we actually give a damn.
 
Talk show hosts, online influencers, media personalities, sports icons, etc.—do you have a loyal audience that consistently watches you and listens to what you have to say? Do they trust you? Monetizing is matching a trustworthy personality with a winning offer. We pride ourselves in being the worlds’ best at matching winning offers with trustworthy creators for longterm monetization.

What Kind Of Offers?

Offers can be as simple as cool merch matched with a winning promotion, like a truck giveaway. Offers can also be a hot new product that everyone wants.

What kind of products?

Any product that would potentially vibe with you and your audience. From apparel, to consumables (supplements, coffee, etc.), to any kind of hard good. The sky ain’t the limit, we shoot for the moon.

 Front end monetization with promos and hot products is just phase 1 though. Phase 2 involves creating a recurring subscription model for long term scale and consistent revenue.

 There is no one better than us at this. 

Why do we say that so confidently?

Because we want it more than our competitors. Bigly team members aren’t victims and don’t give excuses. Fake bullshit and half truths don’t work with us. We leave ego at the door and aren’t scared to try new things and fail along the way.

You know what happens when you fail enough times?

You gain knowledge from failure and optimize. If you fail enough times in business, you eventually figure out what the f*ck you need to do to make a living.

About Us
My passion for FPV (First Person View) began the moment I discovered it. The excitement, the perspective, and the freedom it offers captured me instantly — and that passion has never faded. I started flying FPV drones in late 2011, beginning with a fixed-wing aircraft equipped with a simple camera and map overlay. Since then, I’ve witnessed the FPV industry evolve at an incredible pace.
 What started as a small team has now grown into a company of over 100 dedicated individuals. We’re committed to providing pilots with high-quality FPV drones and components. As drones become more integrated into everyday life — from personal hobbies to professional use — we strive to meet the needs of racers, freestyle flyers, cinematic creators, and commercial operators alike.
 We firmly believe in the bright future of the FPV industry, and we’re excited to be part of its journey.
 Vision
To lead the future of intelligent FPV drone technology.
Flying has always been a human dream — and it’s ours, too. From day one, our mission has been to help young people achieve their dream of flight. Through years of development and experience, we’ve created a wide range of FPV drones and components. Our goal is to make FPV more accessible, inspiring more people to discover the joy of flying.
Future Outlook
Technology often disrupts and reshapes industries — and FPV is no exception. We see exciting opportunities for innovation: lighter and stronger frames, more efficient motors, clearer VTX transmission with longer range, and smarter flight controller systems.
We believe the FPV industry is just getting started. The future is bright — and we’re ready for it.

Somewhere along the way, we started dreaming: What if we could do this for the rest of our lives?

It wasn’t just about graphic design. It was about being available—for our church, for people, for wherever God needed us to be. We didn’t see ourselves stuck in a 9-5, too busy to serve. We wanted the freedom to say yes whenever ministry called. That truth hit us hard one day at a funeral.

One of our friends—someone who had once praised God so passionately at youth camp—had passed away. There we were, standing in front of grieving family and friends, leading worship. And in that moment, we knew—this is what life is about. Being there. Showing up. Using what God gave us to bring hope.

That’s why God Inspires exists.

We’re not just here to sell Christian clothing. We’re here to inspire you to use what God has placed in your hands. Whether you're an artist, musician, writer, speaker—whatever your gift is, use it for His glory. You were made for more than just going through the motions. You were made to make an impact.

Wearing God Inspires isn’t just about style—it’s about making a statement. A reminder that you’re part of something bigger. A movement of bold believers who aren’t afraid to spread the Gospel. Because the Bible says no word from God comes back empty, and even if someone just reads your shirt, that seed is planted.

Together, we can take His name further. Together, we can spread the Gospel.
Until Heaven is Full.

 
SLOGAN

Until Heaven Is Full

MANIFESTO

We are the chosen ones. The church. The hands and feet of Jesus. With God inspired gifts and talents we will serve others and expand God’s kingdom. Giving Glory to the One who gave it all, we’ll give our all.

MISSION

To equip and inspire disciples of Jesus to boldly use their gifts for God’s glory. Through powerful designs and faith-driven messages, we create more than just clothing—we create a movement. A movement that encourages believers to step out, live unashamed, and spread the Gospel until Heaven is full.

 VISION

To see a generation of bold believers rise up—fearless, creative, and unashamed of the Gospel. We envision a world where every disciple of Jesus walks in their calling, using their talents to make an impact, spark conversations, and lead others to Christ through every opportunity God gives them.

GIVING BACK
Being in a small church is a challenge because we have limited resources. But thanks to  your purchase, we will be able to make a bigger impact and bigger things within our community. You can learn more of our ministry here: www.facebook.com/iglesiamirto

Robert & Mario G.
Founders

BRAND STORY
Where Nature Meets Resilience

For years, I've lived at the intersection of concrete jungles and untamed wilderness. As an outdoor industry veteran and endurance athlete, I've chased sunrises on marathon trails and conquered mountain peaks that touch the clouds. Yet it was during countless nights under office fluorescents that I discovered my most profound truth: our modern lives hunger for wildness.

The 2020 pandemic became our collective wake-up call. As the world held its breath, I watched urban dwellers rediscover neighborhood trails and professionals trade neckties for hiking boots. We weren't just seeking exercise - we were starving for that primal connection where rustling leaves drown out ringing phones, where dirt paths erase spreadsheet grids.

This is where our story takes root.

We craft gear for those who measure life in summit views and finish lines. For the spreadsheet warriors who find salvation in trail dust, and the city dwellers who heal through forest bathing. Our products aren't just equipment - they're bridges between boardroom and backcountry, designed by someone who's navigated both terrains.

Every stitch in our jackets carries memories of alpine winds that cleared pandemic anxieties. Each ergonomic backpack curve remembers moonlight ultramarathons where runners became tribes. We understand because we've lived it - the transformative power of nature that doesn't just refresh your body, but rewires your soul.

In a world that glorifies burnout, we champion trail dirt as the ultimate status symbol. Because true wellness isn't found in sterile gyms or productivity apps - it's waiting where cell signals fade and wildflowers bloom.

Join us in rewriting the narrative. Your next breath of mountain air might just be the revolution you've been seeking.

ABOUT US
Why did we start?
One day in 2017, Roger was driving the lawn mower to weed in the yard as usual, but the machine suddenly stopped working. Based on experience, he knew that the battery was broken, because he just bought it for $139 a few months ago. So he can only go to a retail store to buy a battery to complete his weeding work. He went to several shops, but the prices of original batteries are very expensive. He thought that if there is a cheap alternative battery to choose from, it would be great. A few months later, the Vanon brand was born.

After rapidly risen from 2017 to 2021, Vanon becomes a reputed professional manufacturer of high-quality rechargeable batteries and battery-related accessories.

We devoted ourselves to the wide range of power tool batteries and other digital batteries (Like camera batteries, vacuum batteries. UAV batteries etc.) to the worldwide. So far, We have equipped warehouses in the United States, the United Kingdom, Germany, and Australia to provide customers with the best shopping experience

Based on advanced technologies and the aim of satisfactory services, Vanon has always been constantly improving in performance of the products.

Who we are?

Vanon hopes to bring cost-effective batteries to all buyers who don't have brand premiums but need super high quality. We are committed to a wide range of power tool batteries and other digital batteries. We strive for advanced technology and satisfactory service to continuously improve the performance of our products.Currently we have our own warehouses in USA, UK, Australia, Japan and EU countries.
Our goal:

- High quality products 

- Great customer service

- 30 Day Money Back Guarantee

Company: ALLYSELL LIMITED

Address: 94-96 How Ming Street, Kwun Tong, Kowloon, Room A, 2nd Floor, Hongyuan Center, Kwun Tong, Kowloon Hong Kong SAR

How we evolved？

Launched in 2017 and sold in the US

Sales in Australia in 2017

Sales in Japan in 2018

Sales in UK and Europe in 2019

Our plan is to include more countries and share our products with the world.

 Where are we going?

To provide various options of models as replacement for expensive and overpriced oem batteries.
We are confident that our product will be (some models already are ) good as name brand.

If you have any questions, contact us by email: info@vanonbatteries.com

About Us!
Well, hello there! Welcome to XS-Stock.co.uk!

We're a family-run business nestled in the heart of Irvine, a coastal town on the Firth of Clyde in North Ayrshire, Scotland. You know, the place where it's so wet, even the ducks carry umbrellas. But don't worry, we're here to bring a bit of sunshine to your day!

Irvine, our home, is steeped in history. It was once Scotland's 12th-century military capital and one of its earliest capitals. It's been a haunt of Robert Burns, who has two streets named after him in the town. And let's not forget the rumours that Mary, Queen of Scots, stayed briefly at Seagate Castle. We even have a yearly festival, Marymass, in her honour. Plus, it's the birthplace of two former First Ministers of Scotland, Nicola Sturgeon and Jack McConnell.

Our business is a bit like a double-decker bus. On the ground floor, we've got a massive discount store, right in the heart of Irvine. It's in the old B&Q building, and it's so big, you could fit a herd of T-Rexes in there, or maybe a small army of Golden Retrievers. But don't get any ideas, we've already checked, and the council says no to pet dinosaurs.

About
 
Welcome to Fake Tattoos, your go-to destination for all things temporary tattoo artistry! 

Our Journey Through Time

Established years ago, FakeTattoos.com has been a trusted name in the world of temporary tattoos, offering an array of innovative and stylish designs that allow you to express yourself without the permanence of traditional ink. A New Chapter in 2022

In 2022, FakeTattoos.com underwent an exciting transformation. With fresh vision and unwavering dedication, we were acquired by new ownership, injecting new life into our beloved brand. This transition opened doors to a world of possibilities and allowed us to reinvent and elevate the temporary tattoo experience.

Our Promise to You

At FakeTattoos.com, we understand that each tattoo tells a unique story, and we're here to help you tell yours. Our mission is to provide you with the most exquisite and diverse collection of temporary tattoos, whether you're seeking bold, edgy designs or elegant, timeless patterns.

We take pride in offering:

 Unparalleled Quality: Our commitment to excellence remains unchanged. We meticulously select each temporary tattoo to meet the highest standards of quality and safety, ensuring a beautiful and worry-free experience. All of our products are manufactured in a certified safety tested facility located in China.

 Innovation: We're constantly pushing the boundaries of creativity, bringing you the latest trends and exclusive designs that reflect your individuality.

 Customer-Centric Approach: Your satisfaction is our top priority. Our dedicated customer support team is here to assist you every step of the way, ensuring a seamless shopping experience.

 Inclusivity: Temporary tattoos are for everyone, and we embrace diversity in our designs. No matter your style, age, or background, FakeTattoos.com has something for you.

Join Us on This Exciting Journey

We invite you to explore our revamped website, www.faketattoos.com, and discover the world of possibilities that await. From classic to avant-garde, we have a temporary tattoo for every mood, every event, and every individual.

Thank you for being a part of the Fake Tattoos community. We can't wait to be a part of your temporary tattoo journey, and we look forward to helping you express yourself in the most artistic and beautiful way possible.

Here's to the future of temporary tattoo artistry, where creativity knows no bounds.

BE PROUD OF OUR CULTURE
Us Two Tea represents the second generation of Asian Americans - an Asian founded and owned tea brand that promotes our culture, values, and lifestyle. We are a brand that represents quality, authenticity and unity. We want to inspire our next generation to be more confident about our culture and stay true and authentic to who they are - to be proud of being an Asian American. 

TEA IS FOR EVERYONE
“Us Two” means the two of us. It’s about celebrating all sorts of relationships and connecting people together. We want to celebrate all the small moments in life that give us the greatest joy - a kiss, a smile, a laugh, or a burst of creativity - alone or in the company of those we love. We want to make tea culture more accessible to people in the U.S and to speak to them in a way that coffee connects people here: inclusive, welcoming and accessible.
A NOTE FROM THE FOUNDER
Tea is at the heart of Asian culture and it has always been a part of my life. Yet the tea brands we know and love are not Asian. I couldn’t help but wonder why. I have lived in the US for 10 years now and I have realized that we cannot just wonder. It is our generation’s responsibility to claim our culture and create a brand that represents us.

Us Two Tea is not a traditional Asian tea brand. We are a reflection of the Asian American experience, a unique combination of the east and west. Unfortunately, being a minority group in the U.S makes us a target for discrimination and racism. Constantly trying to fit in, we sometimes get lost in the process and forget who we are.

I hope this brand encourages our next generation to be more confident about our culture and stay true and authentic to who they are - to be proud of being Asian American. I hope it inspires them to pursue their dreams and gives them the confidence to do what they love. We can dare to defy expectations and stand out, not just fit in. 

ASIAN IS ESSENTIAL, ORIGINAL, INSPIRING, PASSIONATE, SOULFUL AND PHENOMENAL. BE PROUD OF OUR CULTURE BECAUSE IT MAKES US WHO WE ARE.

I have always had a heart for helping others and starting/building new adventures. ABOUT
Since its beginnings in 2008, Voda Swim has been making waves in the swimwear industry. The brainchild of international model and designer Yulia Drummond, Voda Swim's Envy Push Up® Swimwear was created to redefine push up swimwear. Inspired by her inability to find a bikini that flattered her small bust, Yulia teamed up with her husband Dustin to develop a brand to make the most of even the smallest assets.

With a range of bold yet feminine styles in an impressive color range, Voda Swim ensures that every woman can have the utmost confidence in a swimsuit. As Yulia once said, “I spend a lot of time at the beach, but I was always self-conscious about my swimsuit. Whenever I put on a bikini, it looked baggy and I looked shapeless. The bikini tops didn’t provide any lift or support, and made my breasts look non-existent.” 


Hearing her complaints, Dustin encouraged Yulia to simply create her own push-up bikini... and Yulia did just that. The result?

Voda Swim's Envy Push Up® bikini top is a marvel of engineering and design, made to maximize the subtle curves of a smaller bosom and create natural looking cleavage, all while making breasts look up to two cup sizes larger.

Yulia incorporates the Envy Push Up® technology into each design, all while ensuring that every collection offers styles and silhouettes to help women feel their best on the beach. Each swimsuit top features non-removable push up padding, with coverage options ranging from cheeky and Brazilian bikini bottoms to full coverage one-pieces.

EXPERIENCE THE ENVY PUSH UP® SWIMWEAR DIFFERENCE
Yulia says: "At Voda Swim, we love supporting local manufacturing. All Voda Swim suits are proudly made in the USA, with the highest quality imported materials. We strive to provide the best possible quality to women and are always choosing fine quality materials. Swimwear is made using XtraLife® Lycra fabric for chlorine and salt water resistance and all hardware is 14K gold plated."

The Envy Push Up® top ranges in size from 32AA to 34DD, making it ideal for smaller busts, as well as naturally larger busts that require additional lift and support. Bottom sizes range from XS (size 0) to XL (size 10). Find your perfect swimsuit fit, and discover your favorite new push-up swimsuit at Voda Swim today!

ABOUT US

"Take Your Tumbling to PRO Level"
PRO Tumble is a trusted name in Gymnastics, Cheerleading and Acrobatics since 2020. We specialise in Ankle Magnets and Arm Bands, expertly designed to aid in athletes' technique whilst tumbling and stunting as well as a range of tumbling accessories.

PRO Tumble is based in Brisbane, Australia and sells worldwide to individual customers, sporting facilities and studios. Our commitment to excellent customer service and competitive pricing has seen us to build strong partnerships with athletes, coaches and businesses. We take pride in our product quality, expert knowledge of the sports our products are used and customer satisfaction.

OUR STORY

PRO Tumble originated under the name "Tumble PRO" in 2018 and was sold by Australian air track company Tumble Star. There were already ankle magnets on the market in 2018 but Tumble Star Owner Letty Fox was disappointed by the bulkiness, pricing and availability of existing products. She then put her own design of ankle magnets into testing which were more comfortable, effective and available worldwide. Over the next 2 years Tumble PRO went through several prototypes and by 2020 came to the design we know them as today. In 2020 Tumble Star was sold and Tumble PRO was rebranded to PRO Tumble.

PRO Tumble ankle magnets and tumbling accessories are extremely popular all around the world. They are sold to individuals, coaches and gyms. In 2025 any beyond, PRO Tumble will be introducing many new products so stay tuned!

Our Story
Your name, even when shared by scores of others, is your own private one-word poem. It contains multitudes, and it cannot be defined by its meaning alone, but by the spirit it gains through its historic evolution.

We mine and explore the essence of names through rigorous research that traces their linguistic origins, meanings, context and relevancy through time. Part science, part art, our process is intense, scholarly, and driven by our insatiable passion for the curious words human beings call themselves. After all, every name is full of life. Telling its story keeps it alive, and helps us learn not just about each other, but ourselves.

Our products celebrate the essence of our identities by showcasing namely narratives in a beautiful, artistic rendering that's worthy of being treasured for generations. Each represents years of study and countless travels through history as we trace names that span time and geography, from Judeo-Christian narratives in the Old and New Testaments, to the incredible survival of Celtic and Slavic names, to the spread of Germanic names and the historical context of names of Arabic and Sanskrit origins.

Our work has taught us that nothing about a name is accidental. Their significance and survival through history is fascinating. When we pay close attention, we discover a story of beauty.

A LITTLE PIECE OF OUR STORY We are Julia and Pablo, founders of Paint by Numbers. Our story began during a somewhat difficult time, when stress and anxiety became part of our routine. We were looking for something to help us disconnect, and by pure chance, while on a trip, we discovered paint by numbers. The funny thing is that neither of us had been particularly good at painting or crafts, nor had we shown much interest in art. But despite that, this technique captivated us from the beginning. What began as a simple distraction became our way of finding peace and reconnecting with ourselves. This is how Paint by Numbers was born: with the idea of ​​sharing this transformative experience with others. Today we continue with the same enthusiasm, creating kits that allow you to relax, disconnect, and enjoy creating something unique, even if you've never considered yourself "good" at art. Because, in the end, that's what it's all about!

About Us
Welcome to Refuse to Conform Clothing!
Where Your Story Becomes Your Strength

When fitting in feels exhausting—we've created a space where you don’t have to. 

When anxiety feels suffocating—our designs give you space to breathe. 

When your truth doesn’t fit into society's boxes—we stand with you.

Refuse to Conform was born in 2015 not just as a clothing brand, but as an answer to a question that I couldn’t shake: "What if the clothes we wear could heal the parts of us that feel broken by a world that expects us to be something we're not?"

Your Battle Is Our Purpose

The weighted fabric of our ultra-heavy anxiety relief hoodies calms your racing thoughts wasn't an accident—it was specifically chosen to help ease your mind when life feels overwhelming.

I know what living with an anxious mind in a noisy world is like. I've felt the loneliness of not fitting neatly into the boxes others wanted me to be in. 

These experiences are the reason behind every design—they're not random, they’re a way to feel understood, safe, and protected.

You’re Never Alone Here

What started as one person's refusal to conform has grown into a community of over 100,000 people. When you slip on our clothing, you're not just putting on your hoodie, you’re part of a community that understands your journey.

Our customers don't just wear our designs—they live in them, breathe easier in them, find moments of peace in them.

My Promise To You

I'm Charlie—the heart behind every design, every package, and every message. 

In 2023, I took a leap of faith to fully commit to this mission because I believe what we're creating together matters.

For me, this isn’t just a brand—it's personal. 

I’ve faced anxiety, felt overwhelmed, and wanted a safe space to just be. That’s why every piece is designed with these moments in mind—to remind you that you’re not alone.

Join A Movement, Not Just A Brand

Every piece you wear starts a conversation. Every design you choose tells your story without you having to find the words. Every time you refuse to conform, you make it safer for someone else to do the same.

Ready to turn your authentic self into your greatest strength?

Our Story
Meet the Founders

Hi, we’re Indy & Cory- ex sleep deprived stress balls, now masters of relaxation.
Back in 2017, our stress levels were seriously getting the better of us...

Restless nights, fatigue and anxiety — we experienced it all. 

Drained and frustrated, all we craved was relaxation and consistent, deep sleep. Products or supplements with harsh chemicals or toxins weren’t an option, we wanted a natural solution to our stress sorrows. 

So what did we do? 

What anyone does when they have a problem these days. We Googled it. 

“Best way to get to sleep naturally, calm anxiety and reduce stress”. 

It wasn’t long before we came across research on deep pressure stimulation and the benefits of weighted blankets. But as we searched the web for a premium quality, affordable weighted blanket in New Zealand…

Crickets. 

So, we started Sleep Heavy the same way so many other incredible ventures are born — through wanting to solve our own problem! 

After experiencing the benefits for ourselves, we quickly realised how impactful our blankets were for improving sleep, reducing stress and helping people live healthier, happier lives, which has been our mission since the beginning. 

Hearing about the dramatic improvements in sleep that our customers are seeing, especially those living with sleep deprivation, insomnia, anxiety, sensory processing disorders, ADHD and PTSD drives us to keep doing what we’re doing. 

Become a master of relaxation with us, and try out a Sleep Heavy blanket today.

Our Goal: Healthy Addictions
We Created Maju Because We Had To

This is Ryan, Co-Founder of Maju Superfoods.

Years before we were known for our Black Seed Oil, Apple Cider Vinegar Gummies, Maca, & more, we were students searching for solutions to our problems.

Back in 2013, I was enrolled in law school down in San Diego, and constantly finding myself absolutely stressed and panicky over exams and did not have time to take care of myself. 

(Law school tends to do that to people, and I was another victim. Maybe you are going through some stress as well?)

Instead of running from the problem, I tried to find other solutions. I tried many things such as cutting out carbs completely (ended up super exhausted because I did not replace it with another viable energy source, such as fat), and drinking hundreds of cups of coffee per month. I found myself constantly crashing and falling asleep in lecture, which wasn't going to cut it in this hyper-competitive environment.

Embarrassment, Fatigue.
After getting embarrassed a few times in class, I knew something had to change...

Then I met with a close friend who had been involved in juicing, and I discovered spirulina. I started slowly with Spirulina, as the taste was a bit odd...but it grew on me. Spirulina helped me feel better and quickly became a daily routine for me-- a healthy addiction.

In my deep dive into health after Spirulina I also discovered many other natural products with histories dating back thousands of years, including Black Seed Oil, Moringa, and medicinal mushrooms (not the kind that make you trip).

Our Friends Started to Notice...
My co-founder and I are experimenters by nature so we tried dozens of different products trying to finds things that works for us.

We felt better and were basically shouting from the rooftops, telling all of our friends what we were up to.

The thing is, we did not have a reputable source to refer them to.

As we searched for quality Spirulina, Black Seed Oil, and other herbs we noticed there was little transparency and quality control.

...We did not feel comfortable sending our friends to Jack's Magical Healing Shop in the middle of nowhere where Jack does not even understand what a Certificate of Analysis is!

There are lots of middle men in the industry that do not truly care about the quality of what they sell, they are simply in it to make a quick buck.

And that's why we created Maju Superfoods. 

We want to help our friends and customers create healthy addictions with potent herbs, oils, and superfoods from around the world.

THE MAJU MOTTO:
Our motto and goal will always be to make it easier for you to add healthy addictions to your life.

We also take very careful considerations as to where our superfoods are grown–as quality and purity is a direct correlation to how, what, when, and where our superfoods are cultivated.

We promise to never lower our standards to cut cost, we are devoted to finding the finest raw ingredients and only offer the best and highest-quality finished products out there so you can create healthy addictions in your life.

About
Our Brand
Triquetra's
Approach To Health
One of our core mottos is “Discovered in nature. Optimized by science.” This is based on the belief that we come from nature. We are not separate from it; within nature is all the abundant bounty we need to achieve optimal health.
Discovered In Nature
Optimized By Science
Like Sir Francis Bacon, we believe science is the exploration of nature. The scientific method is the process of objectively establishing facts through testing and experimentation. Every great natural discovery must be refined through the stringent scientific method. Some in the medical machine would like you to think that science and nature are at odds. But science allows us to identify, refine and optimize the bounties provided by nature.

Health is not just physical – we also have mental, emotional, social, and spiritual needs. All of these areas comprise our overall health: being unwell in one aspect affects you in all the others. We believe in whole-being wellness.

It's time to take your health into your own hands and start living the life you deserve. We all have the right to a healthy life free from barriers and obstacles, and Triquetra has found the highest quality, most ethically grown resources Mother Nature provides to help you achieve that goal. Connecting with the natural world can renew our mind, body, and spirit. We can find balance and recovery. We can create harmony in our lives. It's time to start living a healthy life full of vitality and joy. Use mother nature as your guide and Triquetra as your accomplice on your journey to wellness. Health is your birthright! Claim it today!

At the young age of 22, Sean Gill, founder of Triquetra, found himself scared, confused, and sick. He was on his 12th day in the hospital, suffering from a multitude of different conditions; blood clots throughout his body (including pulmonary embolisms), lymph nodes the size of golf balls, kidney issues, terribly chronic fatigue, and significant gut conditions.

Before this complete health breakdown, Sean worked tirelessly for a tech startup, clocking an average of 75 hours per week. He lived on fast food and coffee, and like the American business culture likes to promote, he naively thought the “grind” was a noble feat and his health was just taking a temporary backseat.

Sean went to the hospital because he knew his body was truly shutting down. The doctors were simply baffled; after countless testing for many chronic diseases, including cancer, they merely shrugged their shoulders and said, “we have no idea.” They proceeded to prescribe him multiple medications and sent him on his way.
After leaving the hospital, he felt dejected and lost. A distinct disease may not have been crippling Sean’s body, but he felt like he was dying. He had no answers. He had no path to get better. All he had was a bag of medications, an extensive list of side effects, and a reminder to “Come back if things get worse.”

But what about getting better? What about getting back to feeling energized and healthy and 22? The medications were just treating the symptoms. What about the causes?

This pivotal moment created a hunger for answers to these questions for Sean. Sean turned to educate himself on the concepts of holistic health, whole body health, integrative and plant-based medicine, diet’s role in health, meditation, the importance of mental & spiritual health… You name it, he read books, researched, and centered his life around it.

Welcome to the rodeo.
Cowboy Colostrum, a bicoastal wellness brand rooted in nature, rowdiness, and wholesome living, pays homage to the essential bond our ancestors forged with bovines. We specialize in premium colostrum supplements sourced from grass-fed cows, delivering a unique wellness experience through larger serving sizes, affordability, unrivaled quality, and delicious milky flavor profiles. At Cowboy Colostrum, we are not only committed to offering a distinctive approach to well-being but also prioritize calf welfare, ensuring a sustainable and balanced perspective on wellness. Our brand celebrates the enduring legacy of the primal connection between humans and bovines, bridging the gap between traditional practices and contemporary wellness.

How it all began
We’re Jessy and Steph. We started Cowboy - here’s why.

The wellness world can feel wildly confusing and contradictory. Search any diet trend, supplement or food religion and you’ll find yourself down a rabbit hole of overwhelmingly convincing information as to why that very thing will either heal you or hurt you.

Our health journeys have been unfolding parallel to one another’s since our friendship formed years ago. We’ve ridden the entire spectrum from vegan to carnivore - from intermittent fasting and yoga to HIIT training and ice baths to dozens of daily supplements and overpriced bodywork. We’ve tried it all, and where we’ve landed is somewhere in the middle.

Humans have a funny way of complicating things - more doesn’t always equal better, and sometimes the simplest of approaches yield the most potent results. We’re big fans of Mother Nature and everything she has so perfectly architected within and around us.

Through bouts of diet changes leading to deficiencies and low energy, we knew something had to change. It turned out that strictly eating plants didn’t lead to perfect energy levels, animal fats actually made us feel strong, and consuming high quality, well sourced protein balanced our bodies in ways that cutting these things out never quite could. We were onto something with the whole animal based approach - what if these primal ways of feeding our bodies held the codes to simply feel good in our bodies? It was time to retire the futile pursuit of looking at our health as an impossible Rubik’s cube to be solved.

Enter colostrum - the ultimate primal nourishment. Nature’s first food. This milky white powder simply.. felt right. We’re taught to listen to our guts, and our guts are huge fans of this golden superfood, so much so that we knew we had to make it more accessible to those around us and spread the good word. So.. here we are now. We’re happy to have you on board.

We’re not making any crazy claims that this supplement will give you wings, heal all your interpersonal relationships or have you sleeping 10 uninterrupted hours a night. We’re suggesting that you too can reap the benefits of nature in her most original form - from a boost in immunity to glowing skin and enhanced athletic performance, colostrum has you covered.

Thanks for being here.
Your cowgirls

OUR STORY
SIMPLER Hair Color was born from the frustration of dyeing my own hair and beard. I exercise and eat right to keep my body and mind feeling young and vibrant. But I got grays early, in my twenties. Sometimes I’m proud to rock my grays, but other times I prefer how I look without them. So, I began casually dyeing my hair & beard using the box-dye brands found at stores.

I hated the messy and complicated process of dyeing my hair and beard at home. It was intimidating and felt like I was conducting a science experiment in my bathroom. And, the dyes burned my skin, which made me worry about the long-term effects the ingredients were having on my body. I tried salons, but they took too much time and money, and in some cases, burned my scalp even worse.

So, having started and sold a few companies before, I did what entrepreneurs do. I decided to create a product that solved my own problem. I traveled the world, from Italy to Germany to Japan to Thailand and more, testing different products and speaking to top hair color chemists, all while searching for a gentler formula with safer ingredients, a thicker dye that didn’t drip, and a single product I could use for my hair, beard, and touch-ups, instead of having to buy 3 separate products. It was also important to me that I create a product I could reuse, with each application feeling as fresh, and being as effective, as the first, in a package that was environmentally responsible, and finally, I wanted to make the entire user experience SIMPLER.

After much research, I found a team of formulators with years of experience making tried and trusted hair products, and a track record of creating safer, premium dyes, to create exactly what I’d been looking for. As I talked to men who dyed their hair and beard, and those that hadn’t but were curious, I heard many of the same frustrations and realized I wasn’t alone. I really believed and hoped that our product could help other people as well.

To accomplish this, I also wanted to build a brand committed to treating customers the way I want to be treated. That’s why we offer FREE Shipping and FREE returns, hassle-free. So here you have it, a SAFER and SIMPLER hair & beard dye to help you look your best, without the harm, fuss, and mess.

Happy Coloring,

ABOUT MOTHER’S EARTH  Mom & son  on a mission   Written by: Lisette Gutker de Geus  Last update: 22 March 2024   Done with large corporations not taking responsibility for the negative impact they have on our planet and its inhabitants, Lisette decided to take action in her own hands....   I was always very consciously recycling and reducing my plastic consumption until I found out that most plastic is not recycled at all  At best, only 32.5 percent ¹ of plastic is recycled in Europe. Several studies have shown that much of the plastic sent in for recycling ends up in landfills, or is incinerated.  This means that even with all our effort, we are barely making a difference. Also, more plastic is being produced now than ever before. So, with your best intentions, you are rowing against the current....  The big multinationals could make a difference here, but they do nothing to little to reduce the damage they do to our planet. What matters to them is profit   Also, many of those still engage in unethical practices regarding humans & animals. Did you know that animal testing on cleaning products is still allowed in Europe?  Besides the fact that plastic is very harmful to our planet, researchers are also finding out more and more about how harmful it is to our health.²   In 2021 and 2022 alone, more than 400 publications were published on the health effects of microplastics.  - Diabetes  - Obestias  - Infertility  - Low IQ + concencration   - disorder in children  - Breast cancer  The list goes on...  I knew there had to be a way to produce the products we use everyday without harming our environment, animals and people....  To leave a better world for our children, grandchildren, and further generations to come  With the help of my son, Floris, we developed the first product of our cleaning line. An environmentally friendly and great smelling detergent with enormous washing power, with which we could take on "the big boys"   We believe that companies should not only strive for profit, but also fulfill their duty to the environment, animals, people and society at large.  From that point on, we have dedicated ourselves to reducing plastic waste, and giving back to people and animals in need, to really make a difference, and are now giving others the opportunity to do the same.  Every time you use a Mother's Earth product, you reduce plastic waste and help a person or animal in need. Together, we turn a simple daily activity into something impactful and meaningful

Our story
I love my Kindle. 

Before our son Archie was born, I’d spend hours reading with it. 

So during those late nights of nursing a newborn, I’d pass the time with my Kindle. 

But late one night, in a haze of sleeplessness, I accidentally dropped my Kindle.
And it landed on poor Archie’s head!

It was upsetting for everyone. 

The next day my partner Ben, made a crude Kindle strap out of an old silicone mat and some staples. With this new strap attached, there was no way I could drop my device. 
Even if I fell asleep, the Kindle stayed in my hand.

And so the very first Strapsicle prototype was born!

A simple idea now a global phenomenon

In just three years our little Aussie business has since gone on to become a worldwide viral sensation - even featuring on Shark Tank! 

We’re now helping hundreds of thousands of people read in comfort. And we absolutely live for all the wonderful comments and feedback we get from our incredible Strapsicle community. 

We’ve even heard from customers with mobility issues like carpal tunnel, arthritis and cerebral palsy tell us how great it is to be able to read again! And that makes me so happy. 

Because I think everyone should have the right to read.
And in my opinion, there’s nothing better than a good book ;) 

Happy reading,

Welcome to Hesacore
Beyond the Ordinary Grip
We believe in pushing the boundaries of innovation to enhance the performance and comfort of racket athletes worldwide.

THE GRIP
The Science Behind Hesacore
Hesacore grip technology, developed through extensive research, addresses common issues for racket sports enthusiasts. Our biomechanically designed hexagonal pattern conforms to the hand's natural contours, reducing harmful vibrations.

Engineered to enhance protection, comfort, grip, and performance.

Traditional 8-edged handles misalign with hand anatomy, lacking lateral support and finger alignment, especially for modern spin techniques. Proper use of the bottom three fingers, with the little finger as the fulcrum, is crucial. The index and thumb aid in controlling and speeding up racket head rotation.

Hesacore's hexagonal pattern enhances friction, allowing a looser grip and preventing slipping. This relaxation extends to the wrist and forearm, resulting in smoother, more powerful shots.

Our Story

Hello! I’m Carina, a Brazilian product designer living in Amsterdam. My love for nature, animals, and caring for the environment has been a big part of my life since childhood, thanks to unforgettable summers at my Austrian grandmother’s farm (on the top photo) in Brazil.

My grandmother was truly special. As a pioneering organic farmer, she embraced a simple, sustainable lifestyle. She grew most of her own food, mended clothes by hand, and used plants for natural healing. Every bit of waste was turned into compost to enrich her farm’s soil.

Inspired by her sustainable practices, I’m committed to carrying on her legacy by reducing single-use plastics and offering toxic-free products that care for both your body and the planet.

In 2019, I had a wake-up call: I learned that most plastic isn’t actually recycled - only 9% globally, and just 50-60% in the Netherlands. Wanting to reduce my own waste, I struggled to find eco-friendly alternatives in regular stores.

Conversations with friends and parents at my kids' school made it clear that many people were unaware of or unconcerned about their plastic waste.

That’s when Beewise was born - with a mission to make sustainability simple and accessible. We help people make conscious choices by offering reusable, non-toxic, and eco-friendly alternatives to everyday products, all with compostable brown kraft paper packaging.

Beewise products are now in over 140 stores across 17 countries in Europe and the US, with our community steadily growing.

We believe small daily changes can lead to big impacts. Join us on the path to a greener future - one mindful choice at a time!

About us
Derived from the Greek words "ekriktikós" and "kínisi", meaning "explosive" and "movement", our goal at Ekrin Athletics is to help athletes achieve just that - explosive athletic movements. We embody this ethos every day as we focus on finding ways to improve muscle recovery, blood flow, and range of motion.

EKRIN ATHLETICS MISSION
Our only focus is to leverage cutting edge science and technology to help people move better, prevent injury, accelerate recovery, and maximize their performance potential.

Ekrin Athletics was founded in 2019 by former collegiate athletes seeking to bring their knowledge and experience in maintaining a fit and healthy body to others. With this goal in mind, Ekrin Athletics was created – a company focused on improving athletic performance through muscle recovery and injury prevention. Ekrin Athletics collaborates with pro and collegiate athletes and trainers to help design tools that meet their high standard of performance. Today, Ekrin Athletics is managed by a small but dedicated team to bring wellness products to people every where.

Welcome to Tut Empire
Where Passion Meets Performance

At Tut Empire , we believe that every step, every move, and every moment is an
opportunity to celebrate the fusion of passion and performance. Established
with a vision to redefine the world of sports wear, we embark on a journey
where style meets functionality, and innovation intertwines with comfort.

Our Story :

Born out of a shared love for sports and a commitment to quality, TutEmpire was founded on the principle that activewear should not only enhance athletic performance but also reflect the unique spirit of the individuals who wear it. Our story is one of dedication to crafting apparel that seamlessly blends cutting-edge technology with timeless design.

What Drives Us:

At the heart of our brand is an unwavering commitment to excellence. We are driven by the belief that everyone, from the weekend warrior to the seasoned athlete, deserves access to sports wear that empowers them to achieve their personal best. Each stitch, every fabric choice, and the meticulous attention to detail in our designs is a testament to our commitment to quality and authenticity.

Innovation Beyond Boundaries:

We strive to push the boundaries of innovation, constantly exploring new materials and technologies to bring you sports wear that not only performs exceptionally but also stands out in a crowd. From moisture-wicking fabrics to ergonomic designs, our commitment to innovation is reflected in every product we offer.

More Than Just Apparel:

Tut Empire is more than a label; it's a community. We celebrate diversity, inclusivity, and the unique stories that make each individual extraordinary. Through our products and our platform, we aim to inspire a community of like-minded individuals who share a passion for an active and vibrant lifestyle.

Our Promise:

When you choose Tut Empire, you're not just choosing activewear; you're choosing a commitment to quality, style, and the pursuit of your personal best. We stand behind our products, and we stand with you on your journey to a healthier, more active life.

Thank you for being a part of the Tut family. Together, let's celebrate the joy of movement, embrace the thrill of progress, and redefine what it means to live an active life. Tut Empire

About Us

In the heart of California, a state known for its beauty as much as its challenges with wildfires, a couple embarked on a journey to make homes safer and emergencies more manageable. We are that couple, and our mission began in our very own living room, after witnessing the devastating impact of fires on communities across our state and beyond.

Our business isn't just about selling fire blankets; it's about fostering a community that's better prepared, more protected, and deeply cared for. With every fire blanket we sell, we're not just offering a product; we're providing peace of mind, a shield against the unexpected, and a testament to the power of proactive safety.

Our journey into the world of fire safety was born out of a desire to make a tangible difference. Having seen the aftermath of fires and the difference timely action can make, we decided to step into the fray, armed with knowledge, compassion, and a relentless drive to change the narrative around fire safety.

Our Mission
To empower individuals and families across California and beyond with the tools, knowledge, and confidence to protect their homes, loved ones, and communities from the threat of fires. Our fire blankets are designed not just for safety, but for the peace of mind that comes from knowing you’re prepared for the unexpected. We strive to be more than a business; we aim to be a lifeline in times of need, ensuring that every household has access to affordable, effective, and easy-to-use fire safety solutions.

Our Vision
Our vision is a future where fire safety is a given, not a luxury. A world where every home, regardless of location or income, is equipped to handle emergencies with calm and efficiency. We envision our fire blankets in homes, schools, and workplaces, acting as silent guardians against the threat of flames. By raising awareness, educating our communities, and providing top-notch fire safety products, we aim to significantly reduce the damage and despair caused by fires. Together, we can build a safer, more resilient world, one fire blanket at a time.

Join Us on Our Journey
As we continue to grow and reach more homes across the country, we invite you to join us in our mission. Whether you’re looking to protect your own home or contribute to a larger cause, your support makes a world of difference. Together, we can turn the tide against fires, creating safer, happier communities for generations to come.

Welcome to Kawaii Stop!

Where Kawaii Meets You!
We meticulously curate the finest selections from Japanese and Korean fashion to enhance your everyday style.

Join our community, championing sustainable kawaii fashion and celebrating cuteness and positivity.

Discover the heart of chic kawaii style with us. Embrace our eco-friendly journey and the captivating charm of Harajuku trends. 🌸

How It Started
Kawaii Stop's journey is a tale of passion, discovery, and a deep-rooted love for the kawaii aesthetic. Over 15 years ago, our founder set foot in South Korea for work. The vibrant streets, bustling with life and color, introduced him to a world of fashion and culture that was both enchanting and unique. As he delved deeper into the local lifestyle, he found himself irresistibly drawn to the region's distinctive style and ethos.

His travels soon took him to Japan, the heartland of Kawaii Culture. Here, he was not just introduced but wholly captivated by the culture of cuteness that Japan so proudly showcased. From the bustling streets of Harajuku to the serene corners of Kyoto, every experience added a new layer to his growing fascination. The adorable trinkets, the childlike charm in everyday items, and the sheer joy of the kawaii lifestyle became an obsession.

Upon returning to the U.S., he felt a void. The conventions, anime, and gaming events he attended couldn't quite replicate the authentic kawaii experience he had grown so fond of. Recognizing the lack of genuine kawaii outlets, he was inspired to bridge this gap. He envisioned a space where others, too, could experience the magic of kawaii without having to travel miles.

Thus, Kawaii Stop was born. More than just a store, it became a haven for all things cute, lovable, and undeniably kawaii. Our founder's experiences in South Korea and Japan, combined with his commitment to sharing the wonders of the kawaii world, shaped the very essence of Kawaii Stop.
How It's Going
Today, we proudly celebrate over five years of spreading kawaii joy and fashion to thousands of enthusiasts around the world. From our humble beginnings to becoming a leader in the kawaii fashion scene, our journey has been fueled by an unwavering dedication to quality and authenticity. With our headquarters in Sheridan, Wyoming, and a dedicated customer service hub in Chicago, Illinois, we are committed to bringing the magic of kawaii closer to our customers. Our team meticulously curates every product, ensuring it embodies the true spirit of kawaii.

Our Story
"Our family is passionate about working together to grow and make  " America's Most Healing Turmeric". We respect  what nature made."

 Ed and Diane Taylor along with members of their family began The American Turmeric Company after they learned how to gently coax the miracle compounds from turmeric. They discovered the ancient wisdom of fermentation techniques that released turmeric's healing potential when it is combined with specific herbs. No chemicals or heat are needed. When modern fermentation is used this time-proven technique makes it possible to enhance and preserve the amazing potency of turmeric.

​They have now added the family's third generation as granddaughters Cristina Taylor and Carla Taylor (shown in this video) serve as the Director of Marketing and Content Management, respectively.

​When their first farm was full of turmeric plants, they ate fermented turmeric daily. It was snappy, orange, and bitter. After a few months, something happened quietly. Diane's pain from gout was gone. Medication was stopped. Family members who suffered from the same condition soon received turmeric and had the same results. They learned that an enzyme in turmeric stops the build-up of uric acid, which causes gout. This one event led them into a very serious investigation of turmeric’s plant physiology and biochemistry.  

​Turmeric's potent compounds are better absorbed when fermented. 

​Many ferments landed on the ceiling before they learned how to design a system that controlled turmeric's power.  Since turmeric has potency in its fibers, they experimented until they had a ferment that would reduce the fibers and release turmeric's potency. Fermentation produces probiotics that build the gut microbiome which initiates turmeric's delivery throughout the body.
