Welcome to Engino!
The home of the inventor who sparked a STEM revolution.
Our story began in 2004 with a passionate teacher, Costas Sisamos, who refused to settle. He saw a problem - students were struggling to create and innovate during their Design & Technology classes in Cyprus schools. With grit, determination, and a lot of heart, Costas developed the first sketches of his idea for modular plastic connectors and 3D-printed prototypes. Despite facing financial challenges and skepticism from others, he refused to give up on his dream. And thus, Engino was born - a tool for education that links technical knowledge with pedagogical training, helping children develop critical life skills such as problem-solving, critical thinking, collaboration, and creativity.

But Engino is more than just a construction toy - it's a philosophy. We want children to be able to solve problems based on their abilities without getting trapped in the construction part, which can lead to frustration and lack of interest. With Engino's snap-fit system, there's no need for cutting chopsticks or using screws and tools, making it simpler and more enjoyable for kids to build and innovate.

About us
Our mission

Asorock (AR) Fragrances believes everyone should smell their best and we set out to make that a reality by providing premium fragrances available for everyone at unbeatable prices.

As fragrance connoisseurs and socially conscious individuals, we realized that perfumes were being sold for way more than they cost to make and  we couldn’t turn a blind eye to the price markup of the industry.  

Craftmanship

All of our perfumes are crafted as extrait de parfums, meaning they are long lasting scents which have a 30-40% concentration of fragrance oil and are among the most highly concentrated fragrances in the market. We source our fragrance oils from France, and blend here in the USA, which has been a global leader in the production and development of original luxury fragrances.

🇺🇸 Blended in USA

 Extrait De Parfum

All AR Fragrances are vegan, cruelty free, and made using 100% clean ingredients.

AR Fragrances Community/Team
Based in Chicago, we started out with a mission to create luxury quality fragrances without the high markups. We strive to create the best customer experience possible, and we are always listening and learning from customer feedback.

About Us
I’m Eppie Thompson. I’ve fallen in love with the pleasures of sewing and I’d love to help you do the same. To me, there’s no such thing as people who don’t enjoy sewing. There are simply people who haven’t tried it yet.

The sampler my granny* made for me still has pride of place on my wall. So when some friends announced their engagement a few years ago, I thought I’d try my hand at making one. From the second I pushed the thread through the eye of the needle, I was entranced by the simple, meditative process. I knew I’d found the perfect antidote to my intense, stressful job.

100 years old and still going strong, making beautiful samplers for every grandchild that comes into the family!

About Us
Welcome to E smart way, your trusted source for fun, fast and simple short-distance electric transportation solutions for over 8 years. As China's first online shop dedicated exclusively to micro-mobility, we proudly represent many leading Chinese manufacturers to sell online

We carry a wide selection of electric bicycles, scooters, wheelchairs, skateboards and more, as well as a range of electric motorcycles and exciting new additions like electric cars, electric car conversion kits,and robots. By directly sourcing quality products from our manufacturing partners, we pass the savings on to empower convenient personal micro-mobility through affordable green vehicles. 

Whether you need a fun commute, touring ride or mobility assistance, customers can shop with confidence in our curated selection. As industry pioneers since 2014, we've helped thousands rediscover freedom and independence through micro-mobility innovations. our electric bikes let you enjoy the journey while saving effort. Models range from mountain to road styles, folding options for easy carrying, and fat tire bikes perfect for varied terrain. We also offer e-bike conversion kits to electrify your existing bicycle.


From international students zipping around campus, to families exploring nature trails together on fat tire e-bikes, to seniors regaining self-sufficiency on mobility devices - we strive to redefine everyday travel and recreation.

We also offer a range of electric motorcycles to satisfy those seeking more powerful electric vehicles for both recreation and practical daily use. Models include mopeds as well as more powerful motorcycles capable of highway speeds.


Electric scooters provide an increasingly popular "last mile" solution for navigating campuses and cities. With the rise of ride sharing and accessibility of stand-up e-scooters, people are rediscovering the freedom and accessibility of personal electric transport. In addition to stand-up scooters, we carry seated electric mobility scooters ideal for assisting less mobile individuals like seniors to regain independence.

For those seeking even more recreation, consider our electric skateboards, unicycles and single wheels that let adrenaline seekers dynamically experience urban landscapes in unique new ways. We take pride in curating only the highest performing products to redefine what efficient short-haul transportation can be.

 

Electric Cars & Electric Cars Conversion Kits: Drive into the future with our eco-friendly electric cars or transform your current vehicle into an electric powerhouse.

 

While we began with short-distance transportation solutions such as electric bikes, scooters, our journey has evolved. Today, we are committed to leading our customers into the humanoid robot era, making robotics the core focus of our business.

Shaping the Future with Robotics
Robotics is transforming the way we live, work, and connect. At E Smart Way, we are proud to offer a diverse range of robots designed for personal, commercial, and industrial applications:

Humanoid Robots: These advanced robots are designed to assist with tasks, interact naturally with humans, and revolutionize personal and professional spaces. They represent the future of human-robot collaboration, empowering our customers to embrace smarter, AI-driven lifestyles.
Industrial Robots: Perfect for manufacturing, logistics, and automation, our industrial robots enhance productivity, precision, and efficiency across industries. From robotic arms to automated assembly systems, we provide tools to elevate your business operations.
Service Robots: Ideal for healthcare, hospitality, and retail, these robots streamline operations, assist customers, and provide reliable support in high-demand environments.
Educational and Research Robots: Inspire the next generation of innovators with robots designed for learning and experimentation. These solutions are perfect for schools, universities, and tech enthusiasts.
Why Choose E Smart Way for Robotics?
Leading Manufacturer Partnerships: As a direct representative of top Chinese robot manufacturers, we bring cutting-edge innovation to market at highly competitive prices.
Comprehensive Solutions: From personal assistant robots for home use to robust industrial automation systems, we cater to a wide spectrum of needs.
Accessibility and Affordability: Robotics should be for everyone. We strive to make advanced technology accessible without compromising quality or performance.
Driving the Humanoid Era: Our mission is to help customers integrate humanoid and other robots seamlessly into their lives and businesses, opening the door to a smarter and more efficient future.
At E Smart Way, we see robotics as more than a product line—it’s a movement. By embracing robotics as our core focus, we aim to empower our customers to lead the charge into a new technological era. Whether you’re looking for robots to simplify your daily life, drive business growth, or spark innovation, we have the perfect solution for you. E Smart Way – Your Partner in the Humanoid and Robotic Revolution.

Our Story | Amorium Jewelry

Eons ago, during times of prosperity and joy, artisans of Eagean (now modern Turkey) discovered new ways of manipulating precious metals and ornamenting them with radiant gems and stones. During this hedonistic Epoque, the best stone cutters and metallurgists of Eagean competed to create the most admired pieces of jewelry. Throughout all the Eagean, the city of Amorium's creations stood out both in creativity and technical complexity. Their new creations included carefully handcrafted jewelry so delicate and mesmerizing, that the world had not seen anything remotely like them. For a brief period of time, the world experienced elegance and beauty through Amorium's finest handcrafted jewelry. However, this human-made paradise did not last forever and disintegrated into the abyss of time and with it, the traditions of oriental artisanship once prospered in the city of Amorium were lost forever...until recently.

In 2012, Amorium Store was born from love & passion for jewelry. We wanted to bring the beauty & delicacy of those lost treasures back to the fore. When the market was flooded with imitation, non-real & expensive pieces, we wanted to offer unique, high-quality & affordable pieces to complement any outfit & help you ladies shine brighter. Quality trending jewelry used to be expensive and many women couldn't afford to treat themselves well, we established ourselves as an alternative by optimizing our operations & design process to make fine & delicate jewelry pieces that are affordable & stand the test of time both in style & durability.

For every version of you, shine brighter with Amorium.

Our pieces are available online and in hundreds of boutiques around the world.

We are proudly based in New York.

The RainPoint Brand Story
Our mission is to create more water efficient gardening tools for gardeners, helping to save water while creating more possibilities to simplify your gardening efforts.

Traditional household watering is difficult to track and can result in water waste. The RainPoint Digital Sprinkler Timer series focuses on "streamlining water use". It is a timer with individual valves that automatically waters plants on a schedule and allows you to manually delay watering in case of rain. You can easily control the time and frequency of your water use. Compared to manual watering, you can save up to 50% water with our digital sprinkler timer and make your watering job easy and simple.

The RainPoint WiFi Water Timer series allows you to control your watering anytime, anywhere with the RainPoint APP. The timers have a built-in water flow meter that allows you to not only set up a time-based watering schedule, but also specify how much water to use per watering and end watering when it reaches a specified gallon. RainPoint's exclusive weather technology also allows the timers to automatically skip unnecessary watering, such as automatic rain delays, freeze weather delays, and more. If you equip the timer with a WiFi soil sensor, it will water more accurately based on the detected soil temperature and humidity data, watering only the water your plants need. Compared to the Digital Sprinkler Timer Series, this series offers another 15% or more improvement in water savings.

And the RainPoint Smart+ series is the master of garden irrigation with the new Homgar APP and unique cloud technology that allows all your watering devices to be connected in the cloud, creating a crossover smart home irrigation system for you.

About us

At PadelUSA.com, it's all about the team. We are a group of passionate padel enthusiasts, each bringing unique experience and expertise to the table. As players with diverse levels, styles, and backgrounds, we've united with a common goal: to create the ultimate online padel shop in the USA.

When we started in 2021, the padel market in the USA was still relatively small. We chose to focus on a more restrained selection of top-quality products, carefully sourcing only the best gear available. Our goal was to meet the specific needs of a growing but niche community of American padel players who were seeking reliable, high-performance equipment.

As the sport gained popularity and the demand for padel gear expanded, we grew alongside it. We gradually broadened our offerings to include a wider selection of rackets, shoes, balls, bags, and accessories. Despite our expansion, we have remained committed to ensuring that every item in our store meets the highest standards of quality and performance.

This dedication and growth have led us to become a sponsor of the biggest padel competition that has taken place so far in North America: the WPT Miami Padel Open! Our involvement in this prestigious event underscores our commitment to the sport and to supporting the padel community in the USA.

At PadelUSA.com, we partner with top brands like Adidas, Babolat, Bullpadel, Head, Nox, Osaka, Siux, Slazenger, and Wilson, offering a selection of equipment that has been rigorously tested by top players. Each product is backed by the official guarantee of the supplier, so you can trust that you're getting genuine, high-quality gear.

Our commitment goes beyond just providing the best products. We pride ourselves on delivering an exceptional shopping experience, with fast and reliable delivery, a user-friendly website, and a team that's always available to assist you. We know how important it is to have the right gear, which is why we continuously test and approve new products to ensure our inventory remains the best in the market.

So if you're looking for the best service, the best selection, and the best online padel shop for the American market, look no further than PadelUSA.com.

We hope our products help you dominate the court while looking your best. Time to hit the ball like a pro.
